                     <interp inst="t18301028-140-person1202" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I stopped the prisoner with this ham.</p>
               <p>ROBERT PURSSORD. I have no doubt this is my ham, but I cannot exactly swear to it - a lad is here who saw him take it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301028-140-person1203">
                  SAMUEL 
                  WILCOX
